      <title>[Android]通过Intent启动另一个一个Activity</title>
      <link href="/posts/b67e66a5/"/>
      <url>/posts/b67e66a5/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>一、调用setClass()方法：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Intent intent = new Intent();</span><br><span class="line">intent.setClass(MainActivity.this, Activity_second.class);</span><br><span class="line">startActivity(intent);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>二、通过设置组件setComponent()，也称为显式Intent：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Intent intent = new Intent();</span><br><span class="line">intent.setComponent(new ComponentName(&quot;com.example.android\_intent\_1&quot;, &quot;com.example.android\_intent\_1.Activity_second&quot;));</span><br><span class="line">startActivity(intent);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>三、隐式Intent：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Intent intent = new Intent(&quot;com.example.android\_intent\_1.intent.action.Activity_second&quot;); </span><br><span class="line">startActivity(intent);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
