      <title>[Android]Activity间传递数据的两种方法</title>
      <link href="/posts/a729367a/"/>
      <url>/posts/a729367a/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>一、传递简单的数据 用到的方法：putExtra(); 在MainActivity中声明并传递：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Intent intent = new Intent();</span><br><span class="line">intent.setClass(MainActivity.this, SecondActivity.class);</span><br><span class="line">/*传递简单的数据-start**************/</span><br><span class="line">intent.putExtra(&quot;str&quot;, &quot;Data!!!&quot;);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>在第二个Activity（SecondActivity）中获取： 一般用以下方法</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">/*先取得与当前activity关联的Intent，再获取数据*/</span><br><span class="line">getIntent().getStringExtra(&quot;str&quot;);</span><br><span class="line">String data_1 = getIntent().getStringExtra(&quot;str&quot;) + &quot;&amp;lt;-SecondActivity的第一种获取&quot;;</span><br><span class="line">Log.i(TAG, data_1);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>当然也可以用这种：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">/*使用Bundle去获取*/</span><br><span class="line">Bundle bundle = getIntent().getExtras();</span><br><span class="line">Log.i(TAG, bundle.getString(&quot;str&quot;) + &quot;&amp;lt;-SecondActivity的第二种获取&quot;);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>二、传递较为复杂的数据（例如boolean类型） 通过对象Bundle携带并传递数据。 用到的方法：putExtras(); （注意和第一种用到的方法，名称上只相差了一个字母“s”）。 在MainActivity中声明并传递：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Intent intent = new Intent();</span><br><span class="line">intent.setClass(MainActivity.this, SecondActivity.class);</span><br><span class="line">/*传递相对复杂的数据-start**********/</span><br><span class="line">Bundle data = new Bundle();</span><br><span class="line">data.putBoolean(&quot;boolean&quot;, true);</span><br><span class="line">intent.putExtras(data);</span><br><span class="line">/*传递相对复杂的数据-end************/</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>在第二个Activity（SecondActivity）中获取：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">/*使用Bundle获取*/</span><br><span class="line">Bundle bundle = getIntent().getExtras();</span><br><span class="line">Log.i(TAG, bundle.getString(&quot;str&quot;) + &quot;&amp;lt;-SecondActivity的第二种获取&quot;);</span><br><span class="line">Boolean data_2 = bundle.getBoolean(&quot;boolean&quot;);</span><br><span class="line">/*传递的是boolean值，所以相应的用getBoolean()方法*/</span><br><span class="line">Log.i(TAG, data_2 + &quot;&amp;lt;-SecondActivity复杂数据的获取&quot;);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
